item.description:
I've been wanting to play one of my favorite courses, so decided to just book a tee time. I was able to round up one of my regular golfing buddies and decided to post here to see if we could get a couple others to join us. I have played here several times. It is a difficult, but fair course. The greens can get quite tricky on a few holes. I think it's a fun place to play.

Details:
Atkinson Country Club

Rates: $62 ($80 with GPS cart)
